<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>其他快捷设置css属性值的方法</title>
    <script src="http://www.anydo.wang/resource/js/jquery-3.1.1.js"></script>
    <style>
        body{
            text-align: center;
        }
        .test1{
            margin: 30px auto 0;
            width: 80%;
            border: 2px solid red;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .div1{
            width: 200px;
            height: 200px;
            background-color: #2aabd2;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .test2{
             width: 80%;
             height: 200px;
             margin: 50px auto 0;
             overflow: auto;
             border: 1px solid red;
             text-align: center;
         }
        .test3{
            width: 1500px;
            height: 200px;
            margin: 50px auto 0;
            overflow: auto;
            border: 10px solid blue;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: #2a6496;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="test1">
    <div class="div1"></div>
    <button id="btn1">检测</button>
</div>
<div class="test2">
